	"description": "<p>Adds a bonus to concentration saving throws based on the multiplier in the change value (<code>@prof * N</code>):</p><ul><li><strong>0</strong> — <code>@prof * 0</code> — No bonus.</li><li><strong>1</strong> — <code>@prof * 1</code> — Proficiency bonus.</li><li><strong>2</strong> — <code>@prof * 2</code> — Double proficiency (expertise).</li></ul><p>To change the level, edit the change value and replace the multiplier with 0, 1, or 2.</p>",
